TopicTitle: Looking for an old mod that had a bucket wheel excavator in it

Articles.Content: I remember a mod that added a lot of inventory parts, and the only part i remember is a small drill that looked like a bucket wheel excavator that was reddish in color, and could be placed in an inventory. If anyone knows what the mod is please tell me
Haven’t used this mod in a while, so I might be wrong, but i think a mod that fits your description would be https://spacedock.info/mod/2558/Capsule Corp. - Kerbal Kolonization Program
